TheCurrencyCloud,is,an,international,payment,provider,that,provides,payment,conversion,and,exchange,services,TheCurrencyCloud,API,allows,users,to,make,REST,calls,to,get,access,to,the,API,execute,a,currency,trade,create,and,maintain,payment,beneficiaries,make,international,payments,access,exchange,rate,information,and,group,settled,trades,The,API,will,have,access,account,management,and,contact,information,in,the,future,An,account,is,required,with,service